  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1325870/extras/4418b27e77571ce8a199c70a8e0cd855.poster.avif?t=1621186482\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1325870/extras/4418b27e77571ce8a199c70a8e0cd855.webm?t=1621186482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1325870/extras/4418b27e77571ce8a199c70a8e0cd855.mp4?t=1621186482\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Kotel Ne Gori is first-person action-adventure game taking place in Samozbor Universe. Vanquish your opposition with rakes!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Plot</h2>Princess of Gigacrush was abducted and imprisoned into nine magical orbs. Only Kotel and his friends can rescue her.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game contains:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Endless amount of rakes to fire on your adversaries<br></li><li> Nine game stages to complete<br></li><li> Six enemy types to chase you<br></li><li> Faithful comrade follower that illuminates up your path<br></li><li> Lots of breaking bars in half<br></li><li> Circular saws moving on the floor<br></li><li> The Princess who is waiting for You to save her</li></ul>",
